**Score rationale per gap point:**

| ID | Evidence | Why not higher |
|----|----------|----------------|
| 1 Spec Quality | Brief passed verbatim to `claude -p spec` in `sessions.py:run_build()` line ~88; no decomposition, no ADW routing | No PITER classifier wired |
| 2 Context Precision | `fetchRepoContext()` fetches up to 60 files sorted by priority heuristic — better than whole-repo dump, but no targeted injection per phase | Same context blob for all 8 phases |
| 3 Model Selection | `config.py:ALLOWED_MODELS` + user-selectable opus/sonnet/haiku; dashboard defaults to sonnet | No auto-escalation between tiers during a session |
| 4 Tool Availability | Full Claude Code tool suite (Bash, Write, Edit, Read) available via `--verbose` subprocess | No MCP tools wired into analysis pipeline |
| 5 Feedback Loops | WebSocket streams raw output; SSE streams per-phase; ResultCards update incrementally | No structured PASS/FAIL gate; evaluator tier absent |
| 6 Error Recovery | `sessions.py:run_build()` sets `status="failed"` and returns on first error — no retry, no fallback model | Single hard-fail path throughout |
| 7 Session Continuity | `_sessions` dict lost on restart; `SESSION_SECRET` regenerates; `handoff.md` is minimal stub | P1-A not implemented |
| 8 Quality Gating | `src/tao/agents/__init__.py` empty; no second-pass evaluator in web flow | Evaluator skill defined but never invoked |
| 9 Cost Efficiency | Claude Max zero-token-cost; `token-budgeter` skill defined; cost shown via `$cost_usd` metric events | Perfect score — no billing exposure |
| 10 Trigger Automation | Manual web UI or CLI only; no `/api/webhook`; no cron; no GitHub Actions integration | Entire trigger automation backlog unimplemented |
| 11 Knowledge Retention | `.harness/lessons.jsonl` absent; `agent-expert` skill defined but inoperable | No cross-session learning possible today |
| 12 Workflow Standardization | ADW templates defined in `skills/agent-workflow/SKILL.md`; `phases.ts` enforces 8-phase structure | ADWs not enforced at brief entry; no intent classifier routes to them |

**ZTE band: 35/60 = Assisted (21-35).** One point below Autonomous threshold. Addressing Error Recovery (+2), Session Continuity (+2), Quality Gating (+2) alone would cross to 41 — Autonomous band.